user_description: Separated from my partner in Australia for nearly 16 months. 70 exemption refusals. #LoveIsNotTourism
text: It's scary to think most people trust Facebook message boards over doctors & scientific journals. No, you shouldn't be forced to take the #CovidVaccine. No, the gov't isn't trying to put a chip in you. Yes, it has been being developed for longer than #COVID19 has been around.

About to speak on @CFRAOttawa about family docs & #CovidVaccine. I have an inbox of 300 messages (we asked what our patients received). One pt refused Moderna at a clinic, asserting that they want to wait for Pfizer. That’s what happens with mixed https://t.co/zpCPTWy75v

The ppl who love to tell you

"I got the #covidvaccine to protect others" 

And also "wear masks for the sake of others"

Same lot who stole all the pasta & loo roll at the start & didn't give 1 fuck about the elderly or vulnerable.
#NoVaccinePassports
